\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/28\/surah-al-fatihah-every-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":35860,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Recitation of Surat al-Fatihah in every prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no prayer for one who does not recite the opening of the Book, Surat al-Fatihah.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 756, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 394 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42945,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/09\/surat-al-fatihah-wajib\/","url_meta":{"origin":35860,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salah: Reciting Al-Fatihah in prayer is obligatory","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 9, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA prayer performed by one who has not recited 'the foundation of the Quran' during it is deficient, deficient, deficient, incomplete.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 395 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25027,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/28\/surah-al-fatihah-enough\/","url_meta":{"origin":35860,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Recitation: Surat al-Fatihah is enough, more is better","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 28, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ata\u2019 reported: Abu Huraira, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIn every prayer is a recitation. Prayers that were recited aloud by the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, we have recited aloud to you, and what he recited silently, we have kept silent with you. Whoever recites\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/35860","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=35860"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/35860\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com